OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1774211656
OL,3,CBelfast Giants beaten 3-1 by Glasgow
OL,4,CClan
OL,6,FThe Belfast Giants had their lead at
OL,7,Fthe top of the Elite League table cut
OL,8,Fto six points after a 3-1 defeat to
OL,9,FGlasgow Clan at the SSE Arena.
OL,11,FCade Neilson's shot gave the visitors
OL,12,Fthe lead, but the Giants responded
OL,13,Fwell and headed into the first
OL,14,Fintermission on level terms thanks to
OL,15,FJJ Piccinich.
OL,17,FTristin Langan restored the visitors'
OL,18,Flead in the second period and the
OL,19,Fhosts soon fell further behind when
OL,20,FRobert Lachowicz made the most of a
OL,21,Fmisunderstanding in centre ice.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
