FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1774211656
OL,3,CBelfast Giants beaten 3-1 by Glasgow
OL,4,CClan
OL,6,FThe Clan come away with the victory
OL,7,Fand the two points, with the sides set
OL,8,Fto meet again on Sunday in Glasgow.
OL,10,FSpeaking after Saturday night's match,
OL,11,FHead Coach Adam Keefe said: "Glasgow
OL,12,Fwas much more ready than us, again
OL,13,Fwe've been humbled in a big way.
OL,15,F"That was maybe the worst display of
OL,16,Fhockey we've played in a long time.
OL,17,FIt's unacceptable. I think we all
OL,18,Fmaybe took our eyes off the ball and
OL,19,Fthat's what happens to you."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/3
